{"data":[{"name":"113:1","price":"（使徒*よ、）言え。「私は黎明¹の主*に、ご加護を乞う。","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡفَلَقِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6226,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「黎明（ファラク）」は、「裂く」という語から派生したものとされる。そこから、「（夜の闇から裂き出される）黎明（家畜章９６も参照）」だけでなく、動物、種子、水など、裂かれて出現する全てのものを指す、といった説もある（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：２５５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-falaqi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) the dawn","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-falaqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1280],[3,1280,2110],[4,2110,3005]]}},{"name":"113:2","price":"かれが創造された物の悪から。","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6227,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri mā khalaqa ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) what","He created","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","mā","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,2040],[3,2040,2380],[4,2380,3595]]}},{"name":"113:3","price":"また、深まった闇（夜）の悪から。","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ غَاسِقٍ إِذَا وَقَبَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6228,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ghāsiqin idhā waqaba ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) darkness","when","it spreads","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ghāsiqin","idhā","waqaba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,3870],[5,3870,4945]]}},{"name":"113:4","price":"また、繋ぎ目に息を吹き込む女たちの悪から。¹","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ ٱلنَّفَّٰثَٰتِ فِي ٱلۡعُقَدِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6229,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　これは魔術師の女たちのこと。魔術を行う際には、紐（ひも）のつなぎ目に息を吹き込んでいたとされる。また、魔術師として特に女性が言及されていることに関しては、「そもそも魔術師が女性なのではなく、『心』という省略された女性名詞にかかっているため」「預言者*ムハンマド*に魔術をかけたユダヤ教徒*ラビード・ブン・アル＝アァサムの娘たちのことを、特に指しているため」（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：７０４－７０５参照）「アラブ人の魔術師の多くは、女性だったため」（イブン・アーシュール３０：６２８参照）といった説がある。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri al-nafāthāti fī al-ʿuqadi ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) the blowers","in","the knots","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","al-nafāthāti","fī","al-ʿuqadi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2150],[3,2150,4440],[4,4440,4630],[5,4630,5935]]}},{"name":"113:5","price":"また、嫉妬¹した妬み屋の悪から」。","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ حَاسِدٍ إِذَا حَسَدَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6230,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「嫉妬（ハサド） 」とは、恩恵を授かった誰かから、その恩恵が消え去ってしまうことを望むこと（ムヤッサル６０４頁参照）。筆章５１訳注内の「アイン」についての説明も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ḥāsidin idhā ḥasada ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) an envier","when","he envies","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ḥāsidin","idhā","ḥasada",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1990],[3,1990,3160],[4,3160,3750],[5,3750,5605]]}}],"chapter":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq","Chapter Al-Falaq","Falaq","Surah Falaq","Chapter Falaq","Al Falaq","Surah Al Falaq","Chapter Al Falaq","Surah 113","Chapter 113","The Daybreak","الفلق"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}